Here is a list of some of the other lot clearing services that we can provide:[/x_text][x_icon_list][x_icon_list_item type="fire-extinguisher"]Clearing out a fire escape[/x_icon_list_item][x_icon_list_item type="recycle"]Restoring animal habitats[/x_icon_list_item][x_icon_list_item type="check"]Providing more visibility of the landscape[/x_icon_list_item][x_icon_list_item type="photo"]Helping to bring more symmetry and/or balance to the landscape[/x_icon_list_item][x_icon_list_item type="road"]Clearing for hunting developments and trails[/x_icon_list_item][x_icon_list_item type="leaf"]Clearing for tree and plant growth management[/x_icon_list_item][x_icon_list_item type="home"]Clearing for power and utility lines[/x_icon_list_item][/x_icon_list][x_text]These are only some of the possible projects that could require tree and shrub clearing. Feel free to contact us for a consultation so that we can discuss options for your particular project. We are an incredibly versatile team that is up for a wide variety of lot clearing projects. Just give us a call so that we can begin to plan out your lot![/x_text][/x_column][/x_row][x_row inner_container="true" marginless_columns="false" bg_color="" style="margin: 40px auto -50px auto; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px; "][x_column bg_color="" type="1/3"  style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px; "][x_image type="none" src="https://www.almileytree.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/tree_care_industry.png" alt="Lot Clearing Tree- Tree Care Industry Member" link="false" href="#" title="" target="" info="none" info_place="top" info_trigger="hover" info_content=""][/x_column][x_column bg_color="" type="1/3"  style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px; "][x_image type="none" src="https://www.almileytree.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/isa.jpg" alt="Lot Clearing Tree- ISA Member" link="false" href="#" title="" target="" info="none" info_place="top" info_trigger="hover" info_content=""][/x_column][x_column bg_color="" type="1/3"  style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px; "][x_i